  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building & Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Civil Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday – Friday 8AM – 5PM, Saturday half day)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $5,500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for all on-site technical and engineering matters</li><li>Participate in project planning and monitor progress and schedules, including preparing work plans, schedules, work procedures, safety analysis, clarifications, managing resources, and arranging procurement.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, consultants, and sub-contractors on project matters, provide solutions, handle documentation, and attend progress meetings</li><li>Ensure all work meets company quality standards and contractual requirements</li><li>Assist the Project Manager with monthly progress claims and reports</li><li>Ensure supervisors, foremen, workers, and sub-contractors meet client and regulatory work requirements</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Civil Engineering or any equivalent discipline</li><li>Minimum 2+ years of construction experience is preferred</li><li>Experience of civil engineering works such as road works, earthworks, drainage works are an added advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76392 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
